news_headline: You are logged in as a TRADER

news_body: The fine for open positions of ELEC-dayX at the end of the day is $20,000/contract.

news_headline: Welcome to the RITC2026 GBE Energy Electricity Trading Case - practice server

news_body: There is increased speculation of small sized factory tenders to BUY electricity from the local market.

Given the expected supply and demand in the market, the Regulatory Authority for Electricity board expects that the price for tomorrow will be between $17.11 and $23.11.

There will be 652 contracts available in the entire ELEC market, 326 contracts for buying and 326 contracts for selling. There are a total of 19 Producers, 19 Distributors and 38 Traders in the market.

Please note that the RAE will charge a bid-ask spread of 1 cent
